Package com.onlinepayments.sdk.client.android.asynctask

Interface PaymentProductAsyncTask.PaymentProductCallListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
Session
Enclosing class:
PaymentProductAsyncTask
@Deprecated public static interface PaymentProductAsyncTask.PaymentProductCallListener
Deprecated.
use PaymentProductResponseListener instead to also receive callbacks with error information.
Callback Interface that is invoked when the Payment Product request completes. In case of an error and/or exception, the onPaymentProductCallError(ErrorResponse) callback will be invoked. On success the onPaymentProductCallComplete(PaymentProduct) callback will be invoked.
